high_descs: Go left and the right to face the plant on the ground in front of the window.
Pick the white pitcher off of the floor next to the plant.
Turn around and go forward and then left towards the lamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Turn a lamp on with a pitcher in hand.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the window.
Pick up the white watering can that is on the floor below the window.
Turn around, walk across the room, hanging a left behind the black sofa, and walk up to the little white table in front of you.
Turn on the lamp that is sitting on the little white table.
anns.task_desc: Inspect a watering can using the light of a lamp.

high_descs: turn to the left and go forward a few steps and turn to the left and go to the end of the rug and turn right and take a step and turn to the left and take a step
pick up the tea pot from the floor
turn to the left and take a few steps and turn to the left and go to the wall and turn to the left and go to the lamp on the table
turn on the lamp on the table
anns.task_desc: Examine a tea pot by the light of a lamp
